tory'),(123,'Molecular Gastronomy','Caviar that tastes like blueberry? Lemons (no sweeteners added) that taste like lemon candy? Chocolate mousse that disappears in your mouth, leaving only the delicious flavor behind? Come make some, eat some, and learn about the science behind these treats!',100,NULL,'New House (W70), House 6 (French House), 5th floor kitchen','2010-04-08 22:00:00',60,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','dormitory'),(124,'Dessert Night: S\'mores','Join us in the Next House courtyard to toast s\'mores! Come enjoy the chocolate-marshmallow-graham cracker goodness as we share some entertaining MIT tales.',100,NULL,'Next House (W71), Courtyard','2010-04-08 22:30:00',90,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','dormitory'),(125,'Poker Tournament','Come relax and play poker at LCA for a prize. Take Boston West saferide to the 3rd stop, or call 516-503-2875 for a ride from campus.',100,NULL,'Lambda Chi Alpha, 99 Baystate Rd., Boston','2010-04-08 22:30:00',90,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','fraternity, sorority, living'),(126,'Ice Cream Social','Ice Cream, Ice Cream, Ice Cream! Who could resist this deliciousness? Enjoy a night of tasty ice cream with everyone as you settle in for CPW! ',100,NULL,'New House (W70), House 4, 5th floor south','2010-04-08 22:30:00',90,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','dormitory'),(127,'Painting, Fondue, and Star Gazing','Come join us for &quot;wall&quot; painting, star gazing, and an expensive cheeses study break!',100,NULL,'Simmons Hall (W79), 4C Hallway','2010-04-08 22:30:00',90,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','dormitory'),(128,'SUGAR HIGH DANCE PARTY','Can you feel the bass? Come dance it up with your future classmates. We have enough sugar to power you through the rest of this crazy weekend. And did we mention glow sticks? Check out http://tinyurl.com/bc-sugarhigh for updates.',100,NULL,'Burton-Conner House (W51), Porter Room','2010-04-08 22:30:00',210,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','dormitory'),(129,'FIREHOSE: Duct-Tape Mania','Want to make a duct tape wallet? Sandals? A fire hydrant? Come make awesome things out of duct tape! Duct tape provided. PRETTY COLORS. Come hang out, eat food, and take classes until stupid late.',100,NULL,'6th floor of building 24','2010-04-08 23:00:00',60,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','academic,class,student, oraganization'),(130,'FIREHOUSE: Burnside\'s Lemma','Want to know how many ways you can paint the faces of a cube with n colors? Abstract algebra can help you--but be warned, this is not the algebra everybody did in high school! ',100,NULL,'6th floor of building 24','2010-04-08 23:00:00',60,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','academic,class,student, oraganization'),(131,'La Casa Study Break','Come after the CPW festival and join us for our weekly study break Thursday night. Our study breaks consist of good food and serve as a fun break from homework and responsibilities. Make new friends and get to know the La Casa familia.',100,NULL,'New House (W70), House 3, Spanish House Dining Room','2010-04-08 23:00:00',90,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','dormitory'),(132,'FIREHOSE: Your Art Teacher LIED to You!','Come see your art teacher\'s claims fall at the hand of experimental science: the science of human vision. This class is part of ESP\'s FIREHOSE Event! Come hang out, eat our food, and take classes until stupid late. ',100,NULL,'6th floor of building 24','2010-04-08 23:00:00',120,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','academic,class,student, oraganization'),(133,'Cocoa and Stories ','Come join Fourth East for an extended version of our nightly cocoa tradition. We provide the hot chocolate, dessert, and MIT stories. Meet in the East Campus courtyard by the ugly modern art.',100,NULL,'East Campus (64), Fourth East','2010-04-08 23:00:00',120,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','dormitory'),(134,'AEPi Cidernight','Hot apple cider, homemade banana bread, lots of other baked goodies, and some fun games make this late night event a can\'t-miss... 5th stop on Saferide Boston West, or call us at 847-902-0863 for a ride.',100,NULL,'Alpha Epsilon Pi, 155 Bay State Rd., Boston','2010-04-08 23:00:00',180,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','fraternity, sorority, living'),(135,'Nightmare','We\'re bringing back our favorite holiday, like Jason and Freddy from the grave. Let your inner monster loose on the dancefloor at Skullhouse. ',100,NULL,'Phi Kappa Sigma, 530 Beacon St., Boston','2010-04-08 23:00:00',180,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','fraternity, sorority, living'),(136,'The 3 P\'s: Pizza, Poker, Pool','CPW has begun: it is time to put on your poker face. Win cool MIT prizes, eat delicious pizza, and test your pool skillz. By the way, no counting cards!',100,NULL,'Sigma Phi Epsilon (the big red door), 518 Beacon St., Boston','2010-04-08 23:00:00',270,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','fraternity, sorority, living'),(137,'Midnight Buffet','Not thinking about calling it a night, were you? Drop by the Kappa Sig stoop instead for a late-night snack, some pick-up basketball or that last game of Wii Olympics.',100,NULL,'Kappa Sigma, 407 Memorial Dr., Cambridge','2010-04-08 23:30:00',90,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','fraternity, sorority, living'),(138,'Room For One More','Watch the modern cult movie \"The Room\" with the residents of the Third HNC. Idolize Tommy Wisseau, and marvel at the intricate twists of the subplots.',100,NULL,'Senior House (E2), Third HNC','2010-04-08 23:30:00',150,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','dormitory'),(139,'Movie on the Roof','Enjoy a movie on our roof deck overlooking the heart of Kenmore Square, the famous CITGO sign, and Fenway Park. Third stop Saferide Boston East.',100,NULL,'Phi Sigma Kappa, 487 Commonwealth Ave., Boston','2010-04-08 23:45:00',135,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','fraternity, sorority, living'),(140,'Late-Night Snack','Got the midnight munchies? Stop by TDC for some late-night grub.',100,NULL,'Theta Delta Chi, 372 Memorial Dr., Cambridge','2010-04-08 23:59:00',60,NULL,NULL,37,'confirmed','fraternity, sorority, living'),(141,'Midnight Frisbee','Come join the brothers of Alpha Delta Phi and hordes of your newfound friends